.DS_Store

# Only the curated featured-client tokens (slug-named) are tracked in
# git. Ad-hoc tokens extracted by the workspace UI are saved under
# their project_id (UUID); those should stay local to each deployment
# so a re-deploy doesn't ship someone else's extraction back to every
# operator. Operator-edited brand text and per-client overrides also
# stay local.
graphic-tokens/*-brand.txt
graphic-tokens/*-overrides.json
graphic-tokens/[0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f]-*.json
